@startuml 08-diagrama-implantacao
skinparam node {
    BackgroundColor #F0F8FF
    BorderColor #2C3E50
}
skinparam artifact {
    BackgroundColor #FFFACD
    BorderColor #2C3E50
}
skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
    BorderColor #2C3E50
}

node "Maquina do Usuario\n(Browser)" as browser {
    node "WebAssembly Runtime\n(.NET 10 WASM)" as wasmRuntime {
        artifact "MathPillars.Web.dll\n(Blazor WASM)" as webDll
        artifact "KaTeX.js\n(Renderizacao LaTeX)" as katex
        artifact "Plotly.js\n(Graficos 3D)" as plotly
        artifact "ScottPlot.WASM\n(Graficos 2D)" as scottplot
    }
}

node "Servidor de Hospedagem\n(ASP.NET Core 10)" as servidor {
    node "Processo ASP.NET Core" as processoApi {
        artifact "MathPillars.Api.dll\n(Web API)" as apiDll
        artifact "MathNet.Numerics.dll\n(Motor Matematico)" as mathnet
    }

    node "Servidor de Arquivos Estaticos" as arquivosEstaticos {
        artifact "wwwroot/\n(Assets Blazor WASM)" as wwwroot
        artifact "index.html\n(Ponto de entrada)" as indexHtml
    }
}

browser -down-> servidor : HTTPS\nREST (JSON) / SSE (text/event-stream)
webDll --> katex : JS Interop
webDll --> plotly : JS Interop
webDll --> scottplot : Uso direto WASM
apiDll --> mathnet : Chamada direta .NET

browser ..> wwwroot : Download inicial dos\nassets WASM (cache)

note right of browser
  Stateless por design.
  Nenhum dado persiste
  entre sessoes.
end note

note right of servidor
  CPU-bound: MathNet.Numerics
  executa SVD, PCA, gradientes
  diretamente no servidor.
  SSE transmite progresso
  em tempo real.
end note

@enduml
